in the design folder there will be have folders which in turn have style sheets for each design concepts
    like for material design there wil have material/b-material.sass
                                            flat/b-flat.css
                                            metro/b-metro.css
                                            cupertino/b-cupertino.css


attribute naming will be discussed

like we will use 
    b-btn for material button
    b-btn for metro button, 
    b-btn for flat button
    and b-btn for cupertino

    but only body will have a class b-material or b-metro or b-flat or b-cupertino


e.g 


b-btn {
    background-color:$m-primary;
    box-shadow: $btn-box-shadow;
}

b-btn {
    background-color: $f-primary;
    // flat buttons use no borders
    // no box-shadow
}

b-btn {
    background-color: $mtr-primary;
    border:$mtr-btn-border;
}



